<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
    <head>
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
        <title>Starbucks Coffee</title>
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.3.7/css/bootstrap.min.css" integrity="sha384-BVYiiSIFeK1dGmJRAkycuHAHRg32OmUcww7on3RYdg4Va+PmSTsz/K68vbdEjh4u" crossorigin="anonymous">
        <link rel="stylesheet" href= "/stylesheets/landing.css">
        <link href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/font-awesome/4.7.0/css/font-awesome.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-wvfXpqpZZVQGK6TAh5PVlGOfQNHSoD2xbE+QkPxCAFlNEevoEH3Sl0sibVcOQVnN" crossorigin="anonymous"> 
    </head>
    <body>
        <div class= "border"></div>
        <nav class="navbar navbar-default">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="navbar-header">
                    <img class="navbar-brand" src="http://wjon.com/files/2014/03/Photo_TBD-320x411_1.jpg?w=600&h=0&zc=1&s=0&a=t&q=89" >
                </div>
                <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="bs-example-navbar-collapse-1">
                    <div class="navBar">
                        <ul class="nav navbar-nav">
                            <li><a href="/coffee">Coffee</a></li>
                            <li><a href="/tea">Tea</a></li>
                            <li><a href="/drink">Iced Drink</a></li>
                            <li><a href="/bakery">Bakery</a></li>
                        </ul>  
                    </div>
                    <ul class="nav navbar-nav navbar-right">
                        <li class="navRight"><a href="/">Layout</a></li>
                        <% if(!currentUser){ %>
                            <li class="navRight"><a href="/login">Login</a></li>
                            <li class="navRight"><a href="/register">SignUp</a></li>
                        <% }else{ %>
                            <li class="dropdown">
                                <a href="#" class="dropdown-toggle" data-toggle="dropdown" role="button" aria-haspopup="true" aria-expanded="false">New Post <span class="caret"></span></a>
                                <ul class="dropdown-menu">
                                    <li><a href="/coffee/new">New Post To Coffee</a></li>
                                    <li><a href="/tea/new">New Post To Tea</a></li>
                                    <li><a href="/drink/new">New Post To Iced Drink</a></li>
                                    <li><a href="/bakery/new">New Post To Bakery</a></li>
                                </ul>
                            </li>
                            <li class="navRight"><a href="#">Signed In as <%=currentUser.username%></a></li>
                            <li class="navRight"><a href="/logout">Sign Out</a></li>
                        <% } %>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                       
            </div>
        </nav>
        <div class="header">
            <div class="jumbotron">
                <div class="container">
                   <h2>Starbucks Coffee and Espresso</h2>
                   <p>Since 1971, it always has been and will always be about quality. We’re passionate about ethically sourcing only the finest Arabica beans and roasting them with great care to craft the best coffee. Our passion for Starbucks coffee and espresso is rivaled only by our love of sharing it.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="middle">
            <div class="jumbotron">
                <div class="container">
                   <h2>COFFEE FINDER</h2>
                   <p>Our coffee masters have distilled their years of tasting knowledge down to three simple questions to help you find a coffee you’re sure to love.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <div class="jumbotron">
                <div class="container">
                   <h2>HOW TO BREW</h2>
                   <p>It’s surprising how different brewing methods can enhance particular characteristics in your coffee. Let us help you unlock the full potential of your coffee—for the perfect cup every time.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.2.1.js" integrity="sha256-DZAnKJ/6XZ9si04Hgrsxu/8s717jcIzLy3oi35EouyE=" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.3.7/js/bootstrap.min.js" integrity="sha384-Tc5IQib027qvyjSMfHjOMaLkfuWVxZxUPnCJA7l2mCWNIpG9mGCD8wGNIcPD7Txa" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
